<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>

<Defs>
  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseWeapon">
    <defName>Weapon_GrenadeNote7</defName>
    <label>Samsung Galaxy Note 7</label>
    <description>An ancient 21st century telecommunication device originating from the planet "earth", where all humanoids, mutant or not, originated from. According to records, while the device failed as the intended purpose as a telecommunication device due to a fault causing the internal battery to explode, this allowed the device to be used as a makeshift bomb, often with powerful results. \n\nDue to a successful recall that took 96% of these faulty devices off the streets of earth, remaining examples became highly sought after and collectable in the planet earth, let alone in the rim, so merchants often pay with kidneys and lungs for a chance to touch this device.</description>
    <tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/Item/Equipment/WeaponRanged/Note7</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
    </graphicData>
    <uiIconScale>1.3</uiIconScale>
    <soundInteract>Interact_Grenade</soundInteract>
	<thingSetMakerTags>
	<li>RewardStandardQualitySuper</li>
	</thingSetMakerTags>
	<tradeTags>
      <li>ExoticMisc</li>
    </tradeTags>
    <techLevel>Industrial</techLevel>
    <statBases>
		<Beauty>3</Beauty>
		<Flammability>3</Flammability>
		<SellPriceFactor>0.80</SellPriceFactor>
		<MarketValue>2000</MarketValue>
		<Mass>1</Mass>
		<RangedWeapon_Cooldown>2.66</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
    </statBases>
    <weaponTags>
      <li>GrenadeDestructive</li>
      <li>EmpireGrenadeDestructive</li>
    </weaponTags>
    <thingCategories>
      <li>Grenades</li>
    </thingCategories>
	<smeltable>true</smeltable>
    <relicChance>1</relicChance>
    <verbs>
      <li>
        <label>throw Samsung galaxy note 7</label>
        <verbClass>Verb_LaunchProjectile</verbClass>
        <hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
        <range>12.9</range>
        <forcedMissRadius>1.9</forcedMissRadius>
        <warmupTime>1.5</warmupTime>
        <noiseRadius>4</noiseRadius>
        <ai_IsBuildingDestroyer>true</ai_IsBuildingDestroyer>
        <soundCast>ThrowGrenade</soundCast>
        <targetParams>
          <canTargetLocations>true</canTargetLocations>
        </targetParams>
        <defaultProjectile>Proj_GrenadeNote7</defaultProjectile>
        <rangedFireRulepack>Combat_RangedFire_Thrown</rangedFireRulepack>
      </li>
    </verbs>
	    <smeltProducts>
      <Steel>25</Steel>
	  <Gold>5</Gold>
    </smeltProducts>
    <comps>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Explosive">
        <explosiveRadius>2.66</explosiveRadius>
        <explosiveDamageType>Bomb</explosiveDamageType>
        <requiredDamageTypeToExplode>Flame</requiredDamageTypeToExplode>
      </li>
    </comps>
  </ThingDef>

	
	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseGrenadeProjectile">
		<defName>Proj_GrenadeNote7</defName>
		
		<thingClass>Projectile_Explosive</thingClass>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Projectile/Note7</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<projectile>
			<explosionRadius >6</explosionRadius >
			<damageDef>Bomb</damageDef>
			<damageAmountBase>400</damageAmountBase>
			<explosionDelay>100</explosionDelay>
		</projectile>
	</ThingDef>
	
	
	
	
	
